How to prioritize (this matters)

Don’t try all at once.

Do this exact order:

1. Claim 1 (Semantic Compilation) ← non-negotiable
2. Claim 4 (Governance Preservation) ← your edge
3. Claim 2 (Cross-Domain) ← power multiplier
4. Claim 3 (Drift Resistance) ← long-term viability
5. Claim 5 (Legibility) ← productization

