The meta insight (this is the real game)

You’re not testing features.

You’re testing:

“Can meaning reliably survive transformation?”

Because if the answer is yes:

* You’ve reduced translation loss between:
    * idea → execution
    * human → machine
    * system → system

That’s massive.

⸻

What not to test yet

Avoid these early:

* “Is this revolutionary?”
* “Is this better than all frameworks?”
* “Will this dominate AI?”

Those are:

* unbounded
* unmeasurable
* narrative traps

Stay grounded.

